       Modifier Layers (7 in OutcomeResolver, 25+ in PlayerAgent.bat()):

       OutcomeResolver (Persona Mode):

       1. Batting Intent Modifiers (lines 32-49): attack/rotate/defend/slog
       2. Delivery Type Modifiers (lines 52-81): yorker/bouncer/slower_ball/googly/etc.
       3. Intent × Delivery Interactions (lines 84-101): e.g., slog vs yorker = +0.06 wicket
       4. Confidence Differential (lines 120-128): batting_conf - bowling_conf
       5. Risk Appetite (lines 131-138): high risk → more sixes AND wickets
       6. Ball Context (lines 206-247):
         - Pressure index (>0.7)
         - Dew factor (<0.85 helps batting against spin)
         - Boundary asymmetry (multiplicative)
         - Experience years (veterans: -0.01 wicket; rookies: +0.008 wicket)
         - Field placement (deep fielders suppress boundaries)

