       5. Pitch Features (Pitch Agent)

       File: /c/Users/prabh/OneDrive/Desktop/gitpk/ipl-panda/ipl-oracle/backend/app/agents/pitch_agent.py

       Per-Over Deterministic Evolution:

       For each pitch type (batting_friendly, batting_paradise, spin_friendly, pace_friendly, balanced):

       - batting_ease (0.2-0.95): how easy to bat (varies by over and innings)
       - pace_effectiveness (0.2-0.95): fast bowler effectiveness
       - spin_effectiveness (0.2-0.95): spinner effectiveness
       - bounce_consistency (0.65-0.85): pitch variability
       - swing_available (bool): overcast conditions
       - turn_available (bool): spin_eff > 0.55

       Over Phases:
       - Early (0-5): pace-friendly, high bounce, some grass
       - Middle (6-14): batting flattens, pitch becomes batsman-friendly
       - Death (15-19): wear factor affects consistency, spinners may grip more

       Second Innings Penalty: +0.08 additional wear → harder to bat

